full_text: RUDLOF'S TRANSLATION SERVICE 77 King Street Sydney Translation from the Slovak N.S.W. Australia Phone: BX 4067 (Original bearing One Crown 5. - .. Duty Stamp) Crowns 3.-- Stamp Duty paid.
